      <title>供应紧张和地缘政治风险导致油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-rise-tighter-supply-geopolitical-risks-2024-03-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一亚洲早盘，油价小幅上涨，巩固了上周的涨幅，当时由于供应收紧，油价上涨了近 4%。]]></description>
